headline: Prime, subprime space divide set to widen in 2025: CBRE
summary: The vacancy rate in prime buildings is expected to reach pre-pandemic levels by 2027, while cost-conscious tenants will drive demand for available Class B and C space, according to the firm’s 2025 outlook.
